creator: Skyline Design LLC
descriptionHtml:
Relapics is online software that is developed to bring together the hierarchical Lineage of people concerning their families and relatives.

It helps a person to look for his ancestors and descendants as well as siblings and other relatives.

Relapics enables these related people to communicate with each other through real-time chatting , events and other posts.
Related people can post information to all other people on the platform, for example in the form of advertisements to boost their businesses.

Download Relapics now and track your family lineage and get united with your People.
descriptionShort: Connect with Family and Friends with Relapics
